(:summary    "Count words in the buffer and in region"
 :created    "2002"
 :updated    "20020418"
 :license    "GPL"
 :authors    (("Dr. Rafael Sepúlveda." . "drs@gnulinux.org.mx"))
 :maintainer ("Dr. Rafael Sepúlveda." . "drs@gnulinux.org.mx")
 :provided   (word-counter)
 :commentary "\
This file has all the functions that create a word counter. It has an
interactive word-counter and can display in the modeline the number of
words in the buffer and in the current region, plus more details.")
